column1: What percentage of the 2022 Chilean referendum vote will be to approve the new constitution?
column5: ['Less than 40.0%', 'Between 40.0% and 50.0%, inclusive', 'More than 50.0% but less than 60%', '60.0% or more', 'Chile will not hold a referendum on adopting a new constitution in 2022']

column6: While the English Wiki entry stopped updating opinion polls, the Spanish one hasn't (and nothing much has changed): https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plebiscito_constitucional_de_Chile_de_2022

No opinion polls updated on Wikipedia in almost 2 months, and I couldn’t seem to find any more that weren’t included. I’m less confident than the crowd that this will resolve in Bin 2. Could go even lower:
